# Retro Arcade Theme

## Color Palette
- Neon cyan `#00FFFF` — primary accent, screen glow
- Neon magenta `#FF00FF` — secondary accent
- Electric green `#39FF14` — success/highlight
- Amber `#FFBF00` — warnings, warm accents
- Deep purple `#1a0033` — background base
- Dark bg `#0a0014` — page background

## Typography
- Headings: `font-pixel` (Press Start 2P) — always uppercase
- Body text: `font-terminal` (VT323) — larger sizes (18px+) for readability
- Never use system fonts or modern sans-serifs

## Glow Effects
- CSS: `text-shadow` with 2-4 layers of currentColor at increasing blur
- Three.js: `emissive` property + bloom post-processing
- Cabinet screens should cast colored light onto surroundings

## Do NOT
- Use modern rounded corners, soft gradients, or flat design elements
- Use smooth sans-serif fonts
- Create static-feeling pages — always include some ambient animation
